Author: Juzion
Title: [ANN][ICO][DBT TOKENS][Datbit Network - Decentralized network]
Body: DATBIT NETWORK [DBT TOKENS]                                    Decentralized network to turn every virtual data into a real commodity.  The Datbit network allows anyone to store structured data securely in a decentralized way on a smart contract blockchain. The DBT smart token enables optional selling and buying of stored data while enforcing data usage rules as set by the data owner.                                     Datbit - The Datbit Network Token  The Datbit token facilitates transactions in the Datbit network, providing value to the data on the network. The Datbit token sale will enable full development of the Datbit network and provide an efficient, transparent and secure smart contract token to facilitate exchange of data on the network.                                      WHITE PAPER : https://datbit.org/Datbit-WhitePaper.pdf                                                                                                                                                                                           Datbit Token Specifications  Specifications: Token name:    Datbit Token Token ticker:   DBT Token type:   ERC20 Total supply:   1000000000 (fixed, no more tokens will be issued) Mining: The concept of a mining is absent, the quantity of tokens after the sale does not change .                                                                                                                                                                                              Datbit Token Crowdsale  Role of Token                 : Enable trade of data between data owners and buyers Symbol                          : DBT Supply                           : 1,000,000,000 For Sale                         :   600,000,000 Emission Rate                 : No new tokens will be created Price                              : 0.01USD (Aprox:30,000 DBT per 1 ETH/0.05 BTC) Sale Period                     : 27/11/2017 to 27/12/2017 (UTC-05:00) Accepted Currencies        : ETH ,BTC,LTC and Altcoins Token distribution           : 26th December to 31th December 2017                                                                                                                                                                                              Project Roadmap  August 2016 - Concept Development: Founders start exploring large scale data storage for IOT devices in the medical and smart home sector and devise first prototypes of structuring unstructured data. July 2017   - White Paper & Concept Validation: With the release of the white paper and the resulting community feedback we have fine tuned the concept and laid out the roadmap for the Datbit Network. November 2017    - Pre-Sale & Alpha Version: The Presale for the Datbit Token started on 27/11/2017, and ended on 27/12/2017. Datbit token allows users to participate in the new data economy. Token distribution from 26/12/2017 to 31/12/2017. December 2017   - Datbit Token Sale: The Datbit Token Sale is planned to launch from 28th December or until the hard cap is reached. Datbit released an early alpha release of the Datbit app before the launch of token sale. The development of the Datbit test network continues . July 2019 - Test Network Launch: The launch of the Datbit test network marks the beta release and will allow basic functionalities to be explored by developers and the community. August 2019   - Release Candidate: The feature complete release candidate will be deployed to the test network and undergo intensive testing and bug fixing over the next three months. November 2018 - Datbit Launch The launch of the Datbit Main Network marks the start of the new data economy. At this point the Datbit Network will consist of the decentralized Storage Layer, the Datbit App, Open API's to submit and consume data and a full fledged trading system.                                                                                                                                                                                               RELEVANT DOCUMENTS  GitHub : https://github.com/Datbit/Datbit-SmartContract Privacy Policy: https://datbit.org/ICO_tokens_presale_privacy_policy_EN.pdf Tokens Sale Privacy Policy : https://datbit.org/ICO_tokens_sale_policy_EN%20(1).pdf General Terms & Conditions : https://datbit.org/ICO_presale_general_terms_&_conditions_EN.pdf   WEBSITE: https://datbit.org/ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/datbit_org TELEGRAM: http://t.me/datbit_org WHITEPAPER https://datbit.org/Datbit-WhitePaper.pdf REDDIT: https://redd.it/7hj5jm  Website Link : https://datbit.org/                                                                                                                                                                                            Listed Exchanges  Listed Exchange: https://bitebtc.com/trade/dbt_btc     https://p2pb2b.io/trade/DBT_BTC
